The invention discloses a display device and method for eliminating reflected light. The device comprises a control unit, an image processing unit, a display screen and a deviation adjustment unit, wherein the image processing unit and the display screen are connected with the control unit respectively. The display screen is a saw-tooth-shaped screen formed by connecting a plurality of display modules. Each display module comprises two display units and a light ray eliminating unit, wherein the two display units form a specific inclined angle. The deviation adjustment unit is located behind the display modules and is used for adjusting the deviation angles of the display modules. The method for eliminating the reflected light includes the steps that (1) perpendicular incidence angles of light rays are monitored in real time through a light ray induction unit; (2) orientation of the display modules are adjusted according to the perpendicular incidence angles of the light rays. According to the display device and method, through the special screen structural design, orientation of the display units can be adjusted according to incident angles of the light rays, and the optimal viewing effect can be achieved; electronic device screens can be observed and operated in bright light conveniently; effective help is provided for protecting the eyesight.
